=== 主題 ===

[[File:Medium_Screen_Shot_2013-01-08_at_9.42.41_AM.png|thumb]]
比起競爭對手[[Posterous|Posterous]]，Tumblr一大優勢就是豐富的主題資源，由於友善的開發套件，許多設計师和開發者都為Tumblr做出高品質的主題<ref>{{Cite web |title=Posterous vs. Tumblr: A Head to Head |url=http://mashable.com/2009/06/29/posterous-vs-tumblr/ |accessdate=2010-05-30 |date=2009-06-29 |work=Mashable |publisher=Jennifer Van Grove |archive-date=2010-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100830235308/http://mashable.com/2009/06/29/posterous-vs-tumblr/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。且在2010年3月24日推出付費主題功能<ref>{{Cite web |title=Introducing the first Premium Themes to the Tumblr Theme Garden! |url=http://staff.tumblr.com/post/470140037/premium-themes |accessdate=2010-05-30 |date=2010-03-24 |work=staff.tumblr.com |archive-date=2010-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100327225457/http://staff.tumblr.com/post/470140037/premium-themes |dead-url=no }}</ref>，這被認為是Tumblr尋求營利的一個手段<ref>{{Cite web |title=Tumblr Starts Offering Premium Themes |url=http://mashable.com/2010/03/24/tumblr-premium-themes/ |accessdate=2010-05-30 |date=2010-03-24 |work=Mashable |publisher=Stan Schroeder |archive-date=2010-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100526014956/http://mashable.com/2010/03/24/tumblr-premium-themes/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。目前已拥有上千款免费主题<ref>{{Cite web |title=New Tumblr Themes |url=http://www.tumblr.com/themes/recent |accessdate=2010-05-30 |work=tumblr.com |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090118210755/http://www.tumblr.com/themes/recent |archivedate=2009-01-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。和20款付费主题<ref>{{Cite web |title=Premium Tumblr Themes |url=http://www.tumblr.com/themes/premium |accessdate=2010-05-30 |work=tumblr.com |archive-date=2010-05-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100522004356/http://www.tumblr.com/themes/premium |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 目錄 ===
受到Twitter會員列表服務WeFollow的啟發，Tumblr在2009年5月16日开放了Tumblr Directory<ref>{{Cite web |title=Introducing the new Tumblr Directory |url=http://staff.tumblr.com/post/108205894/directory |accessdate=2010-05-30 |work=staff.tumblr.com |archive-date=2010-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100830002031/http://staff.tumblr.com/post/108205894/directory |dead-url=no }}</ref>。用户可以给一个Tumblr博客打上标签，然后其他用户可以很方便的查看到自己喜欢的特定博客。

